available_quests.title: Bounty: bandits
available_quests.description: Grenda the Blacksmith is offering a bounty for slaying 4 bandits sighted in the area around Riverside Village.

available_quests.title: Gather: goblin ears
available_quests.description: Barlin the Tavern Keeper needs 12 goblin ears. They believe goblins in default may carry them.

objective.item_to_deliver_description: A package to be delivered to Grenda the Blacksmith. Seems to be from Barlin the Tavern Keeper.

available_quests.title: Delivery: Sealed Package to Grenda the Blacksmith
available_quests.description: Barlin the Tavern Keeper asks you to deliver a Sealed Package to Grenda the Blacksmith, who can be found in Riverside Village (Blacksmith's Forge).

available_quests.title: Gather: raw meats
available_quests.description: Barlin the Tavern Keeper needs 11 raw meats. They believe wolfs in Whispering Woods may carry them.

available_quests.title: Gather: rat tails
available_quests.description: Grenda the Blacksmith needs 11 rat tails. They believe giant rats in default may carry them.
